spec_data.Name: trac-xmlrpc-plugin
spec_data.Description:
This plugin allows Trac plugins to export select parts of their
interface via XML-RPC. It also includes some exported functions
for manipulating tickets, with plans to include interfaces to other parts
of Trac's API.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 10:55:06 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Allows Trac plugins to export their interface via XML-RPC
